## 📂 Two Case Files (self-improving loop, accumulated per project under `.claude/`)

- `.claude/debug-log.md` — running log (append painful-enough cases; Twelve Commandment #8 PRD bugs also tagged `[SKIPPED-PRD]` here)
- `.claude/patterns.md` — the highlights page, **read at the start of every 🔴 session**
- `.claude/root-cause-trees/` — root-cause-tree HTML library

**Threshold of pain** (record only if any one is met, **and the evidence section must be filled in**):
① misjudged the root-cause direction ② adversarial debugging (≥2 different hypotheses falsified) ③ root cause crosses layers

**Better to under-record than to dilute** — `patterns.md` is meant to be read at every session start; diluting it kills its value.
Full three-question self-check, the absolute "don't count" list, and the evidence field format → load skill `sentinel`'s `references/debug_log_template.md`.

